        "Service"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，四个主分支。关于技术域这块，domains下面需要细化到什么程度？我看到有subdomains和nested subdomains的层级关系，还有EmailAddress和apps这两个同级节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "domains",
        "subdomains",
        "nested subdomains",
        "EmailAddress",
        "apps"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，domains保持三层嵌套结构。EmailAddress和apps是技术域下的具体实体类型，不是层级关系。PersonOfInterest这块要丰富一些，需要关联emails、repos、companies，还有social accounts和phone numbers这些追踪维度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PersonOfInterest",
        "emails",
        "repos",
        "companies",
        "social accounts",
        "phone numbers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，PersonOfInterest分支已添加。我注意到还有org memberships和Credentials两个子项，GitHubOrg下面需要展开Repositories、commits和members吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "org memberships",
        "Credentials",
        "GitHubOrg",
        "Repositories",
        "commits",
        "members"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，GitHubOrg结构确认。GitHubRepo需要独立出来，因为它有Committers、branches、forks，而且也有自己的Credentials节点。最后Service分支专门管理凭证体系，Credential下面要有username、token、key、secret四个字段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GitHubRepo",
        "Committers",
        "branches",
        "forks",
        "Service",
